MOVE IN THIS FALL!  Come see our Anastasia Elite Modern Coastal plan by Toll Brothers at Edison at eTown, a gated community! This is Builder inventory on an over sized deep PRESERVE home site. Must see model with builder upgrades and massive additional storage. Designer appointments include UPGRADED WHITE CABINETRY, 12x24 TILE, QUARTZ countertops, OAK STAIRS, and several more designer upgrades throughout! This is a master plan community with all the luxury lifestyle enhancements. Jog to your private park, dog park, yoga lawn!
Restore your lifestyle at Recharge, eTown amenity center and enjoy the pool, state of the art fitness, walking path, yoga and event green, Open 2020.
